2011年6月，在开过电视试播集的记者投票中，恶魔岛被选入八部最令人期待的新剧集中的一部。<ref name=cca>{{cite news | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/critics-choice-awards-honors-8-new-shows/ | title = Critics' Choice Awards Honors 8 New Shows | last = Andreeva | first = Nellie | date = June 9, 2011 | work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] | accessdate = June 10, 2011 | archive-date = 2011-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110627082600/http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/critics-choice-awards-honors-8-new-shows/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]网站上，平均获得63/100的评分。<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/alcatraz/season-1|title=Alcatraz - Season 1|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=14 January 2012|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69LmB5bee?url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/alcatraz|dead-url=no}}</ref>

恶魔岛开播时，有超过1000万的美国观众观看了前两集。但是电视的收视率一路下滑，到第五集时仅有接近700万的观看者。

